peace, wisdom, and purity; it is generally a favorable figure,
but often weak, and where it occurs, you may need to seek
help from other people. It is traditionally a figure ofchas-
tity. Albus favors quiet progress and the use ofintelligence,
and is favorable in most business and financial questions; it
is also favorable for beginnings. It is unfavorable in matters
requiring courage and energy, Or in any situation involving
conflict or disruptive change.
