Divinatory meaning: Puella in a geomantic reading stands
for harmony and happiness that may not last indefinitely;
it is a favorable figure in most questions, but fickle. It is
especially favorable for questions involving love and friend-
ship, and brings a positive answer to any question involving
short-term happiness. Because ofits fickleness, however, it
is unfavorable in any situation where permanence is wanted.
