thing desired is within your grasp. Traditionally, Acquisitio is
a figure ofprudence. It represents gain in every sense, and
favors any situation where gaining something is desired. It is
unfavorable whenever loss is desired, such as illness, facing
things you fear, and getting out of difficult situations.
